If you get my drift.

56
00:07:16,290 --> 00:07:17,280
Is that so?

57
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:19,680
And then, from out of the blue...

58
00:07:19,810 --> 00:07:23,690
...they go and get you, a professor
from Harvard University. No offense.

59
00:07:23,770 --> 00:07:25,170
