Come over here, sitzen Sie. Goodness me.

148
00:14:02,090 --> 00:14:06,000
Thank you, Professor. I'm sorry.
I don't know what came over me.

149
00:14:06,090 --> 00:14:10,560
I know what came over you.
High Anxiety, you've still got it.

150
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:16,400
It's probably the excitement and tension
of taking over this new post. I'm...

151
00:14:16,730 --> 00:14:18,320
...sure it will pass.

152
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:20,720
Bullshit!

153
00:14:22,250 --> 00:14:27,200
These things do not let go.
High Anxiety can be a dangerous enemy.

154
00:14:27,810 --> 00:14:31,560
If left unchecked,
it could cost you your life.

155
00:14:35,650 --> 00:14:36,800
Tomorrow...

156
00:14:36,890 --> 00:14:40,560
First thing tomorrow, we have
our first session of psychoanalysis.

157
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:44,240
My boy, I have not had you on the couch
for a long time.

158
00:14:44,410 --> 00:14:47,840
My boy, I promise, we will beat this thing.

159
00:14:48,370 --> 00:14:49,690
Goodbye.

160
