Only 30 seconds late.
You're so strict.

177
00:17:28,610 --> 00:17:29,840
Gentlemen...

178
00:17:31,410 --> 00:17:33,290
...and Nurse Diesel...

179
00:17:33,530 --> 00:17:36,650
...may I propose a toast?
To our new leader:

180
00:17:37,050 --> 00:17:39,280
Dr. Richard H. Thorndyke.

181
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:41,320
Long may he reign.

182
00:17:42,250 --> 00:17:43,680
I thank you.

183
