you understand.

196
00:18:46,490 --> 00:18:48,840
Dangerously sick people!

197
00:18:59,770 --> 00:19:01,000
Dr. Thorndyke?

198
00:19:01,730 --> 00:19:06,280
Will you be at the Annual Psychiatric
Convention in San Francisco next week?

199
00:19:07,370 --> 00:19:09,090
Yes, I...

200
