00:20:29,370 --> 00:20:31,520
- What was that?
- I don't know.

222
00:20:32,050 --> 00:20:33,040
Come on!

223
00:20:38,450 --> 00:20:41,170
It's coming from Nurse Diesel's room.

224
00:20:42,770 --> 00:20:47,360
Is everything all right in there?
Nurse Diesel! Are you all right?

225
00:20:50,410 --> 00:20:51,440
Yes?

226
00:20:51,530 --> 00:20:55,240
We heard some weird noises emanating
from your room. We were worried.

227
00:20:55,330 --> 00:20:58,720
Weird noises? It was the TV.

228
00:20:59,290 --> 00:21:02,520
