234
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,640
- Good night.
- That was no TV.

235
00:21:43,370 --> 00:21:45,360
- Who was it?
- lt was Thorndyke.

236
00:21:45,490 --> 00:21:49,530
- You're making too much noise.
- I can't help it, you're hurting me.

237
00:21:49,650 --> 00:21:52,120
- You're going too hard tonight.
- Get off it.

238
00:21:52,450 --> 00:21:55,170
I know you better than you know yourself.

239
00:21:55,290 --> 00:21:58,120
You live for bondage and discipline.

240
00:22:00,410 --> 00:22:02,760
Too much bondage. Not enough discipline!

241
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:06,050
You want discipline?
I'll give you discipline.

242
00:22:08,490 --> 00:22:09,600
Yes!

243
00:22:09,770 --> 00:22:11,280
Yes. I'm sorry!

244
00:22:11,530 --> 00:22:13,440
Yes! It feels so good!

245
00:22:36,170 --> 00:22:37,200
Yes?

246
00:22:37,330 --> 00:22:41,240
Dr. Thorndyke,
Dr. Montague is here to see you.

247
